Chilean Government Estimates Easing Inflation in Future Months

-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 
2011-10-07T20:27:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/chilean-government-estimates-easing-inflation-in-future-months.html
Chile is keeping consumer prices
under control and inflation probably will fall in the coming
months, Finance Minister Felipe Larrain told reporters today.
The battle to keep inflation in check is never over, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
